  "title": "Chocolate and Guinness cake",
  "subtitle": "A dark, malt-rich chocolate sponge with cream cheese frosting",
  "excerpt": "A one-tin chocolate cake made with stout: the beer deepens the chocolate flavour and keeps the crumb very moist. Finished with a cloud of cream cheese frosting that sits on the dark cake like the head on a pint.",
